fields.name: More about me
fields.value:
Self-diagnosed high-functioning autistic and probably ADHD too
Love to swim, run, ride bikes 🚲, geek out, theater and dance kid at heart.
Anarchist. Humanist (feminist). Environmentalist. Calling out bullshit wherever I see it.

fields.name: Empty nester life
fields.value:
Everything changed when cancer attacked. 

Most pursuits on hold because my dad is facing myelodysplastic syndrome turned acute myeloid leukemia, so I'm spending all my spare time on him.
